title: Tennis star Genie Bouchard owes a date to a stranger thanks to the Patriots
text:
Tennis star Genie Bouchard owes a date to a stranger thanks to the Patriots That Super Bowl ending took all of us by surprise. Post to Facebook Tennis star Genie Bouchard owes a date to a stranger thanks to the Patriots That Super Bowl ending took all of us by surprise.  //ftw.usatoday.com/2017/02/genie-bouchard-date-super-bowl-bet-boyfriend/   Tennis star Genie Bouchard owes a date to a stranger thanks to the Patriots Adi Joseph , USA TODAY Sports 2:32 a.m. ET Feb. 6, 2017 
Genie Bouchard is a pro tennis star. (Photo: Eric Bolte-USA TODAY Sports) 
So, yeah, we all thought the Falcons were going to win at some point Sunday. But most of us aren't going on a date with a stranger because of it. 
Let us now tell the story, through tweets, of Genie Bouchard and @punslayintwoods. Bouchard is a 22-year-old professional tennis player from Canada who is ranked 47th in the world. 
She is not a professional football gambler.
